            <li>Yellow or flickering pilot light (should be blue)</li>
            <li>Unusual smells when the furnace runs</li>
            <li>Increased energy bills without explanation</li>
            <li>Excessive dust or dry air</li>
            <li>Furnace running constantly without reaching set temperature</li>
            <li>Any carbon monoxide detector alerts</li>
          </ul>

